# Auto-Indexer Generator - Build Any Documentation Site

## What This Is
Templates to automatically create index pages for ANY collection of learning materials.  Pick your style, customize, and share! 

## Template 1: Universal HTML Auto-Indexer (Markdown)

```html name=auto-indexer-markdown.html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>üìö Learning Hub</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/marked/marked.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        : root {
            --primary:  #667eea;
            --secondary:  #764ba2;
            --sidebar-bg: #2c3e50;
            --content-bg: #ffffff;
            --text:  #333;
